  <sect2>
    <title>Installation</title>

    <para>
      Install the package with the following commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr \
            --disable-static &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make -j1 install &amp;&amp;
install -v -d -o root -g root -m 755 /etc/ssl &amp;&amp;
install -v -o root -g root -m 644 apps/openssl.cnf /etc/ssl/</userinput></screen>

