  <sect2>
    <title>Configuration</title>

    <para>
      Most users will want to install <xref linkend='cacerts'/> for validation
      of downloaded certificates. For example, these certificates can be used
      by Git or cURL when accessing secure (HTTPS protocol) sites. Users who
      just want to use LibreSSL for providing functions to other programs such
      as OpenSSH and web browsers do not need to worry about additional
      configuration.
    </para>

  </sect2>

